text: Saša Radulović (born 1965) is former Minister of Economy of Serbia. Saša Radulović may also refer to: *Saša Radulović (footballer, born 1978), Bosnian- Herzegovinian and Australian footballer *Saša Radulović (footballer, born 1984), Serbian footballer *Sasa Radulovic (architect) (born 1972), Canadian architect *Saša Novak Radulović (born 1964), Croatian guitarist
title: Saša Radulović (disambiguation)
